title: Zavdiel's Vegetarian Pizza and Falafel Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Organic, Take-out, Catering, Israeli, Kosher
description: A kosher Israeli take on vegetarian pizza and whole wheat bases. Uses rennet-free cheese and fresh ingredients. Vegan suitable include all pizza base and pita, salads except for coleslaw (mayo), falafel, hummus and tahini sauce, soup of the day, chips (not pre-cooked). Note the pastries have an egg glaze.
